</dl>
<p>Words of the Holy Spirit called the words of God:</p>
<dl>
<dd><a href="http://www.biblegateway.com/bible?passage=1Samuel%2010:10;&amp;version=NIV;" class="external text" title="http://www.biblegateway.com/bible?passage=1Samuel%2010:10;&amp;version=NIV;" rel="nofollow">1Samuel 10:10</a></dd>
