<li><a href="http://www.thechristadelphians.org/htm/books/trinity/trinity_mainframe.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.thechristadelphians.org/htm/books/trinity/trinity_mainframe.htm" rel="nofollow">Trinity True or False?</a></li>
<li><a href="http://christianmonotheism.com/php/media_center/media_displayer.php?mode=tags&amp;data=9" class="external text" title="http://christianmonotheism.com/php/media_center/media_displayer.php?mode=tags&amp;data=9" rel="nofollow">moderated debates: trinitarian vs. biblical unitarian</a></li>
</ul>
